flowRoot.flowPara: Traditional web-based editors (such as Proper, the editor used by Substance.io) come with numerous limitations, due to the nature of HTML's contenteditable attribute. In order to improve consistency, overall-editing experience and for adding new features such as Patches and Inline Annotations (see Requirements) a new editing foundation is necessary.
